name: //?CHOICE/
description:
This is my Choice
I strive to find a better me, a person just and true. I want to live and not just be, to be decent through and through.

I need to be a stronger me, both in body and in soul. It's not a whim, it needs to be, for me to feel whole.

I will be that better me, and that better me will stay. I will be better, they'll see, it's time to seize the day!

A Better Me By Jojoba Mansell /? / 3300x5100
